Synopsis: Defines the email addresses to which the email should be sent.
Description: This function sets the email addresses to which the email should be sent.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
EmailTo -Addresses "user1@example.com", "user2@example.com"
Sets the email addresses to which the email should be sent to "user1@example.com" and "user2@example.com".
